cc:Work.dc:title: Kindergarten Art Mary Joseph Jesus
cc:Work.dc:description: Kindergarten Art Mary Joseph Jesus is an individual based and uncoached picture by a kindergarten child. Mary is in a house holding baby Jesus. Joseph is holding a shepherd's staff. There is a patch on his clothes signifying that they were poor. Other symbols on the picture are a flower, star, sun, and heart. A note saying, "I like Jesus" is added to the picture.
